      "role": "user",
      "content": "i already cleaned it with soap and water. the honey thing is because i read that medical grade honey is actually used in hospitals for wound care to prevent bacteria. if the cut isn't wide open or gaping, is it really necessary to go to a clinic? i feel like i can just do the honey and a tight bandage myself and save the trip.",
